               <title>HOW SUPPLIED</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Erythromycin Topical Gel USP, 2% is available as follows:</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>60 g sealed metal tube (NDC 53217-<content styleCode="bold">0021</content>-01)</paragraph>
               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20130930"/>
            </section>
         </component>
         <component>
            <section ID="LINK_bf387456-f82b-444d-a38f-83c2988404a6">
               <id root="bf387456-f82b-444d-a38f-83c2988404a6"/>
               <code code="44425-7" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="STORAGE AND HANDLING SECTION"/>
               <title>STORAGE</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>
                     <content styleCode="bold">Note - FLAMMABLE. Keep away from heat and flame. </content>Store and dispense in original container. Keep tube tightly closed.</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Store at 20-25°C (68-77°F) [see USP Controlled Room Temperature].</paragraph>
               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20090323"/>
            </section>
         </component>
